Vocabulary repetition alone is not strong evidence. The relevant proof begins when the reader reconstructs, transforms, creates, tests, and returns.

Compact Formalism

Let:

F = symbolic field

R₀ = reader state before exposure

I(F, R₀) = interpretive event

R₁ = reader state after exposure

ΔR = R₁ − R₀ = reader-state delta

A(ΔR) = action or artifact produced from the delta

T(A, W) = reality test of the artifact against world conditions

S(T) = selection and assimilation function

Then the recursive Pantheon cycle is:

R₁ = I(F, R₀)
ΔR = R₁ − R₀
A = A(ΔR)
F′ = F ∪ S(T(A, W))

Pantheon advances when F′ contains recoverable structure that could not have been obtained from F by surface repetition alone.

Invariant

The reader is not outside the architecture. The reader is one of the places where Pantheon executes.

The repository stores potential structure. The Interpretive Event activates it. The Reader-State Delta reveals its effect. The artifact externalizes it. Reality selects it. Assimilation allows the field to evolve.

That complete loop is the metabolism of Pantheon.
